Package: synfig
Version: 0.61.07

Revision: 1001

Maintainer: Hisashi T Fujinaka <htodd@users.sourceforge.net>

Depends: libxml++2-shlibs, libsigc++2-shlibs, imagemagick10-shlibs, libdv4-shlibs, libavcodec1-shlibs, freetype219-shlibs, fontconfig2-shlibs
BuildDepends: fink (>= 0.24.12), etl, libxml++2, libsigc++2, imagemagick, imagemagick10-dev, libdv4, libavcodec1-dev, freetype219, fontconfig2-dev, openexr-dev, pkgconfig
GCC: 4.0

Description: Vector-based 2D animation renderer
Homepage: http://synfig.sourceforge.net/
License: GPL

Source: mirror:sourceforge:%n/%n-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: c18c23abe8db6d856f39fe1617e05612

InstallScript: <<
	find %d -name "*.la" -exec perl -pi.bak -e 's| %d.* | |g' {} \;
	make install
	mkdir -p %i/share/%n/examples/walk
	install -p -m644 examples/*.sifz %i/share/%n/examples
	install -p -m644 examples/walk/*.lst %i/share/%n/examples/walk
	install -p -m644 examples/walk/*.jpg %i/share/%n/examples/walk
	install -p -m644 examples/walk/*.sifz %i/share/%n/examples/walk
<<

DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING INSTALL NEWS README examples

DescDetail: <<
synfig is a vector based 2D animation renderer. It is designed to be capable of
producing feature-film quality animation.

This package contains the command-line renderer, the GUI animation editor is in
synfigstudio.
<<
